        "action": "Review use of the '\"Child in Need\" label by social workers & local authorities",
        "additional_details": "We also want:\r\n- Clear differentiation between \"Child in Need\" (CIN) due to disability and CIN due to harm.\r\n- Recognition of systemic and institutional failures as potential safeguarding concerns.",
        "background": "We think the government should have a full, urgent review of how safeguarding applies to disabled children. We want respect and compassion for parent carers doing their best under impossible circumstances.",
